HEADWORD: brainstorm
<hw>brain"storm`</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the clear (and often sudden)
understanding of a complex situation; a sudden brilliant
insight.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> insight, brainwave.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

