==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: brainstorm
<hw>brain"storm`</hw> <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>to try to solve a
problem by discussing it exhaustively in an intense group meeting
encouraging uninhibited and spontaneous contributions from all
members.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> practice brainstorming.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>brain-teaser</ent>⟦br⟧
